data.description: Welcome to this spacious Cape Cod property. This home features high ceilings on the main level, 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 2,976 sq ft of living space and a two car detached garage to make your own! There are two main floor bedrooms with an additional two bedrooms upstairs with a full bath. The kitchen's ample countertop space is great for entertaining. Appliances are included in the sale, including the washer and dryer. Previously renovated, it's a must see. Schedule your showing today!
